      "orig": "Two dialogs may not have been cleared out correctly when the user closed the dialogs, which could cause a problem when CPRS tries to shut down.",
      "text": "Two dialogs may not have been cleared out correctly when the user closed the dialogs, which could cause a problem when CPRS tries to shut down.",
