      "meta": null,
      "label": "text",
      "prov": [],
      "orig": "An access violation occurs on shut down, but because Windows activates the screen saver due to inactivity, the user is not warned that the problem occurred. The workstation does not display the access violation or any other message. If this situation exists and the user signs back into the workstation, CPRS continues to function as if a time-out had not occurred.",
      "text": "An access violation occurs on shut down, but because Windows activates the screen saver due to inactivity, the user is not warned that the problem occurred. The workstation does not display the access violation or any other message. If this situation exists and the user signs back into the workstation, CPRS continues to function as if a time-out had not occurred.",
